   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 21, the 23rd Epeiph. (Give) from the account of Julius Theon and Julius Theon, alias to Papo(), manager of the epoikion of Heraklas, as salary for Epeiph 24 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 24 drachmas. (3rd hd.) And reduce the amount, toward payment of his debt, by 12 drachmas."</ab>
